{
  "texts": [
    "I performed numerous surgeries, managed complex cases, and learned from my mentors.",
    "**Fellowship Programs** Following my residency, I completed two fellowship programs: one in cerebrovascular neurosurgery and another in spinal neurosurgery.",
    "These one-year programs allowed me to subspecialize in specific areas of neurosurgery and refine my skills in complex procedures.",
    "**Continuous Learning** Throughout my career, I've made it a point to stay up-to-date with the latest advances in neurosurgery.",
    "I regularly attend conferences, workshops, and symposia to learn from experts in the field."
  ]
}